Review Vincent Van Gogh – First Steps – Father’s Day Art Card – Fathers Day Cards Popular Vincent Van Gogh – First Steps – Father’s Day Art Card It’s a great choice Vincent Van Gogh – First Steps – Father’s Day Art Card There are many featuresVincent Van Gogh’s First Steps (after Millet). Based upon a painting by French artist Jean-Francois Millet, This oil on canvas from 1890 shows a child’s first steps as the father puts down his shovel and waits with open arms. Makes a great Father’s Day gift.

Unlike similar stores, Art Lover’s Cafe features classic, high resolution works of art that have been carefully restored, color-balanced & retouched to remove spots & artifacts commonly found in most reproductions sold online.
